We often use the JIRA issues macro to embed tasks & issues on Confluence Pages. By doing so, we often include the component column. 
If we insert a JIRA macro for a certain project and add the column, we cannot sort for the component. Only the standard columns are sortable. 

We would love to see this feature on our Confluence for other columns such as component column as well!

